                <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span className="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 border border-amber-400/30 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
                  <div>
                    <p className="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Credit Counseling</p>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-0.5 leading-relaxed">Must be completed <strong className="text-slate-200">before</strong> your case can be filed. Takes 1–2 hours online. The course fee is typically <strong className="text-slate-200">$15–$25</strong>, paid directly to the approved provider — this is separate from your attorney fees.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
